      "components": [
        {
          "html": "<div style=\"--color-snowfield:#ffffff;--color-coal:#000000;--color-graphite:#1a1a1a;--color-silver-mist:#eeeeee;--color-pebble:#6f6f6f;--color-buttery-yellow:#f7e731;--font-sans:'Inter',sans-serif;--font-mono:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;\">\n  <div style=\"background:var(--color-snowfield);width:600px;padding:48px 32px 56px;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:var(--font-sans);text-align:center;\">\n    <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-bottom:28px;\">\n      <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.025em;color:var(--color-graphite);line-height:1.43;\">The helpful home robot</span>\n      <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.025em;color:var(--color-pebble);line-height:1.43;\">Beta launching late 2026</span>\n    </div>\n    <h1 style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:72px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--color-coal);margin:0 0 40px;padding:0;\">Say hello to Memo</h1>\n    <div style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:var(--color-buttery-yellow);border-radius:9999px;padding:14px 8px 14px 24px;gap:16px;\">\n      <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:16px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--color-coal);white-space:nowrap;\">Join the Founding Family</span>\n      <span style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:var(--color-coal);color:var(--color-snowfield);font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:16px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.025em;border-radius:9999px;padding:10px 20px;white-space:nowrap;\">\n        Apply to the beta\n        <span style=\"display:inline-block;width:8px;height:8px;background:var(--color-buttery-yellow);border-radius:50%;\"></span>\n      </span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
          "name": "Hero CTA Banner",
          "role": "",
          "description": ""
        },
        {
          "html": "<div style=\"--color-snowfield:#ffffff;--color-coal:#000000;--color-graphite:#1a1a1a;--color-silver-mist:#eeeeee;--color-pebble:#6f6f6f;--color-earthen-creme:#eadcce;--color-sage-whisper:#aec2b8;--color-buttery-yellow:#f7e731;--font-sans:'Inter',sans-serif;--font-mono:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;\">\n  <div style=\"background:var(--color-snowfield);width:600px;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:var(--font-sans);padding:48px 32px;\">\n    <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:28px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.3;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--color-graphite);margin:0 0 48px;padding:0;\">Built for busy households, Memo works 24/7 to make your life lighter. Hand off your repetitive to-do's, so you can focus on what really matters.</p>\n    <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;\">\n      <div style=\"background:var(--color-earthen-creme);border-radius:12px;padding:24px;\">\n        <div style=\"width:100%;height:120px;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.08);border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div>\n        <h3 style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:18px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--color-graphite);margin:0 0 8px;padding:0;\">Handles the chores</h3>\n        <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:14px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--color-pebble);line-height:1.5;margin:0;padding:0;\">Memo takes on daily repetitive tasks so your household runs smoothly.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"background:var(--color-sage-whisper);border-radius:12px;padding:24px;\">\n        <div style=\"width:100%;height:120px;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.08);border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div>\n        <h3 style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:18px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--color-graphite);margin:0 0 8px;padding:0;\">Always available</h3>\n        <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:14px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--color-pebble);line-height:1.5;margin:0;padding:0;\">Operating around the clock, Memo is ready whenever you need a hand.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
          "name": "Feature Intro Block",
          "role": "",
          "description": ""
        },
        {
          "html": "<div style=\"--color-snowfield:#ffffff;--color-coal:#000000;--color-graphite:#1a1a1a;--color-silver-mist:#eeeeee;--color-pebble:#6f6f6f;--color-buttery-yellow:#f7e731;--font-sans:'Inter',sans-serif;--font-mono:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;\">\n  <div style=\"background:var(--color-snowfield);width:600px;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:var(--font-sans);padding:48px 32px;\">\n    <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.025em;color:var(--color-pebble);margin:0 0 32px;padding:0;\">Frequently asked questions</p>\n    <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;\">\n      <div style=\"border-top:1px solid var(--color-silver-mist);padding:20px 0;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;cursor:pointer;\">\n        <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:16px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--color-graphite);\">What can Memo do?</span>\n        <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M3 6l5 5 5-5\" stroke=\"#6f6f6f\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"border-top:1px solid var(--color-silver-mist);padding:20px 0;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;cursor:pointer;\">\n        <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:16px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--color-graphite);\">Is Memo available for purchase?</span>\n        <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M3 6l5 5 5-5\" stroke=\"#6f6f6f\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"border-top:1px solid var(--color-silver-mist);padding:20px 0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;cursor:pointer;\">\n        <div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;\">\n          <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:16px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--color-graphite);\">How much will a Memo cost?</span>\n          <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" style=\"transform:rotate(180deg);\"><path d=\"M3 6l5 5 5-5\" stroke=\"#1a1a1a\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--color-pebble);line-height:1.55;margin:0;padding:0;\">Memo is designed to be a long-term household investment. Pricing details will be announced closer to the beta launch in late 2026. Join the Founding Family for early access and exclusive pricing.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"border-top:1px solid var(--color-silver-mist);padding:20px 0;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;cursor:pointer;\">\n        <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:16px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--color-graphite);\">How big is Memo? How fast can Memo move?</span>\n        <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M3 6l5 5 5-5\" stroke=\"#6f6f6f\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"border-top:1px solid var(--color-silver-mist);padding:20px 0;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;cursor:pointer;\">\n        <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:16px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--color-graphite);\">Is Memo safe?</span>\n        <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M3 6l5 5 5-5\" stroke=\"#6f6f6f\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"border-top:1px solid var(--color-silver-mist);border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-silver-mist);padding:20px 0;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;cursor:pointer;\">\n        <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:16px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--color-graphite);\">What is the Sunday Beta program?</span>\n        <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M3 6l5 5 5-5\" stroke=\"#6f6f6f\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
